This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it focuses on language learning and representation in a neural model. Additionally, the paper also deals with visual features and their prediction, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of recurrent neural networks suggests that the paper could also be relevant to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning), while the focus on learning and prediction could place it in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
